---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Retaining Walls Cardinia Shire | All Suburbs | Free Quote"
  description="Retaining walls and earthworks across the Cardinia Shire — Pakenham, Officer, Beaconsfield, Berwick, Cockatoo, Emerald, Garfield, Drouin & more. Free fixed-price quotes — (03) 9003 0223."
  canonical="https://pakenhamretainingwalls.com.au/cardinia/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cardinia Shire</span>
      <h1>Retaining walls across the <span class="accent">Cardinia Shire</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Pakenham is the centre, but we work across the whole Cardinia Shire &mdash; from the
        flat new estates in Officer to the steep acreage in Cockatoo and Emerald.
        One free quote, one fixed price, one crew.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All Cardinia Shire suburbs</span>
      <h2>Where we work.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/">Pakenham</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/berwick/">Berwick</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Pakenham South</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Pakenham Upper</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Officer South</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Beaconsfield Upper</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Cardinia (town)</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Garfield</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Bunyip</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Drouin</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Tynong</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Nar Nar Goon</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Cockatoo</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Emerald</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Council requirements</span>
      <h2>Cardinia Shire retaining wall permits.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <p>
          Cardinia Shire Council follows the Victorian Building Authority guidelines on
          retaining walls. The short version:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Under 1m, no load above</strong> &mdash; usually no permit required, but neighbour notification (Fences Act) may apply if it&rsquo;s on a boundary.</li>
          <li><strong>Over 1m, or supporting load</strong> &mdash; building permit required. Engineering computations, soil test, and an inspection.</li>
          <li><strong>Inside the 6m setback</strong> &mdash; planning permit may also be needed if the wall is forward of the building line on a corner block.</li>
          <li><strong>Bushfire-prone areas</strong> &mdash; some Cardinia Shire suburbs (Cockatoo, Emerald, parts of Beaconsfield Upper) require materials compliant with AS 3959 if the wall is part of a defendable space treatment.</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          We handle the lodgement on every job that needs it. The cost is included in
          the fixed quote &mdash; no surprise extras when the council comes back with conditions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Wall types &mdash; one of these is right for your block.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/timber-retaining-walls/"><h3>Timber sleeper</h3><p>Most economical, 15&ndash;40 year lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/concrete-sleeper-walls/"><h3>Concrete sleeper</h3><p>50+ year lifespan, ideal for taller walls.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/block-retaining-walls/"><h3>Block / masonry</h3><p>Premium look, long lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/excavation-earthworks/"><h3>Earthworks</h3><p>Cut-and-fill, drainage, levelling.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Cardinia Shire site visit &mdash; free.</h2>
        <p>Anywhere from Pakenham to Emerald, Officer to Drouin.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Quote online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
